16 May 2012Government will on Thursday 17 May hold a memorial service in honour of the late Minister of Public Service and Administration, Roy Padayachie. Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: 17 May 2012 Time: 11h00 Venue: Tshwane City Hall, Corner Paul Kruger and Visagie Streets, Pretoria Minister Padayachie was accorded an Official Funeral last week , 9 May 2012 at Sahara Kingsmead Stadium in Durban. RSVP: Tshegofatso Modubu Cell: 083 276 0786 E-mail: Tshegofatso@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: Harold Maloka Spokesperson for the Ministry for Performance Monitoring and Evaluation in The Presidency Cell: 082 847 9799 E-mail: harold@po.gov.za /maloka.harold@gmail.comDumisani Nkwamba Spokesperson for the Department of Public Service and Administration Cell: 082 885 9448 E-mail: dumisanin@dpsa.gov.za Issued by Government Communication and Information System